{"tid":2219973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【舊聞】林鄭月娥：全靠新移民撐起香港經濟","createTime":"2020-09-27T09:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T07:11:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":21,"dislike":593,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"ef87ff09d960568f861125e11870479a4fa42e4a","tid":2219973,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"政務司長林鄭月娥表示，香港回歸以來有83萬新移民來港，當中98%是港人內地配偶或子女，因此單程證政策是家庭團聚政策，有存在必要。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，2013年單程證來港人士年齡中位數是33歲，低於全港年齡中位數，當中近九成15歲以上單程證人士有中學或以上學歷，是本港寶貴人力資源，因為在本港勞動力不足下，引入新移民將帶來新動力。<br />\n<br />\n有記者問到部分港人擔心香港「內地化」，施政報告卻提出香港內地融合措施，政府如何處理港人的憂慮，林鄭表示，她相信香港人是理智的，他們會明白香港需要新移民這人口增長的來源，新移民可增加各方面的勞動力，同時部分企業家可開創就業機會，對於香港青年人也是重大契機。"},{"pid":"e76a5d217de7e2d6e0cc4794c04b945717a98448","tid":2219973,"uid":19552,"like":121,"dislike":17,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xtImjAAam1SPBvHr2ZR3TA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-09/01d273d0-0082-11eb-afff-9f9e1c04c33a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxtImjAAam1SPBvHr2ZR3TA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-09%2F01d273d0-0082-11eb-afff-9f9e1c04c33a&h=8973b110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7e99ff2bbc29870cea0e693387d910b565c06f6","tid":2219973,"uid":2002,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"靠你老母"},{"pid":"98947a7755dc7c8b6a12c6a0153296af89b7f959","tid":2219973,"uid":19552,"like":20,"dislike":45,"score":-25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200927/photo/bkn-20200927103735921-0927_00822_001_03p.jpg?20200927112333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200927%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200927103735921-0927_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20200927112333&h=d80e9a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關先生指計劃要求申請人填寫大量文件，對長者而言有一定困難。(李華輝攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200927/photo/bkn-20200927103735921-0927_00822_001_04p.jpg?20200927112333\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200927%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200927103735921-0927_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20200927112333&h=e916ad33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍先生指特地提早1小時排隊，冀能盡早取得津貼。(林敏思攝)"},{"pid":"ab970db1b97351a90270d67f02a717c58f1c2be8","tid":2219973,"uid":19552,"like":75,"dislike":12,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtJ6a92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtJ6a92.png&h=44da6bee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d457662de30c4950aa55b393e6559b63565450ce","tid":2219973,"uid":65747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"7042a5c08c2652aafb470f0506726b6a7dcfd993","tid":2219973,"uid":19552,"like":60,"dislike":9,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKCbngK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKCbngK.png&h=fac09227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ffacd5ef4bbb3c33c198083b69e846bcabcab02","tid":2219973,"uid":304769,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:29.000Z","msg":"呢班含家產食屎啦"},{"pid":"89bc415f2149b241219ef706488f19202cfb0983","tid":2219973,"uid":49336,"like":32,"dislike":12,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e62c97f9358243a2a037f3989d8929dfd943944","tid":2219973,"uid":125017,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"綜援出糧-&gt;消費-&gt;收稅<br />\n內循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e359071f757442b4fbe4465ed74da605b1351